{"tid":365003,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"係時候醒","createTime":"2017-08-19T01:25:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-19T04:57:47.000Z","uid":125861,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5ddf51d8a20ecc958d90e42604f89712dc372085","tid":365003,"uid":125861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T01:25:18.000Z","msg":"時間久了 天空灰了 回不去了<br />\n才驟然醒覺<br />\n想念是一種病<br />\n治不好 活不下去<br />\n<br />\n用盡僅餘的尊嚴 <br />\n用盡全力抓緊衣袖 <br />\n乞求卑微的一撇眼角<br />\n郤被冷淡的漠視與嬉笑<br />\n<br />\n人去了 樓空了 心淡了 <br />\n才驟然醒悟<br />\n真心是一枚禁藥<br />\n忍著痛掏空送人<br />\n破碎只需一秒鐘<br />\n<br />\n硬心腸是最佳良藥<br />\n他很想你 你不想他 他更想你<br />\n很好<br />\n至少不用再哭得<br />\n死去活來"},{"pid":"3c8d87a5cac2d1f53e51f5ef83f19757cc6af5f4","tid":365003,"uid":137659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T04:41:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ff84862d33665a74fc2677dc0f3fc78faf72606c","tid":365003,"uid":73909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T04:47:47.000Z","msg":"我仲未醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7f64f62218798569b552accd261700c95e9eff8","tid":365003,"uid":138388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T04:57:47.000Z","msg":"一切生活如常<br />\n只係要扮作沒有你 我的天空然跟大眾一樣"}]}